<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.8.10">
<l>pāruṇ ṇalla maṟaiyōr nāṅkaip pārttaṉ paḷḷi ceṅkaṇ mālai</l>
<l>vārkoḷ nalla mulaima ṭavāḷ pāṭa laittāy moḻinta māṟṟam</l>
<l>kūrkoḷ nalla vēlka liyaṉ kūṟu tamiḻ pattum vallār</l>
<l>ērkoḷ nalla vaikun tattu ḷiṉpam nāḷu meytu vārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master the ten Tamil [verses] composed by Kaliyaṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">with a fine, pointed spear,</l>
<l>The words a mother spoke about the songs of her simple girl</l>
<l rend="indent">with fine, bodiced breasts,</l>
<l>About bright-eyed Māl of Pārttaṉpaḷḷi in Nāṅkai</l>
<l rend="indent">with the finest Vedic experts on earth,</l>
<l>They will daily gain delight in fine, beautiful Vaikunta.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
